Magicka
pros:
//fast game with modern day graphics with easy controls that moves from location A to B to C and so on
//good amount of action and special effects
cons:
//a lot of difficult battles/boss battles
//some overpowered enemies
//some enemies have unfair attacks
//often times too many enemies fill the screen making it difficult to evade
//your character moves slow
//enemies can stun lock you, instant kill you with spells or attacks, and instant kill you by knocking you out of play
//game lags and crashes
//casting spells is somewhat button combo difficult
//repetitive with increasing difficulty
//some lack of directions/instructions

//good game
